summary: This is a music replacement for the theme at the main menu.
descriptionHtml:
I love the Skyrim main menu theme music however I like to mix things up a bit and I decided to change it to this song. I think it fits very well with Skyrim and thought I should share it.

Sample : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2XItoJ9WPDE

Zelda and all related music is owned by Nintendo. The Zelda temple of time song was remixed by http://bezo.newgrounds.com/
author: bezo
